measurements.description:
Two full flowers on two inflorescences average 16.6cm;
	dorsal sepal cream, caudae light orange distally, striped burgundy, purple hirsute;
	lateral sepals light orange to orange caudae distally, dark burgundy stripes, purple hirsute;
  petals cream;	


	lip dark burgundy;



	substance firm; texture velvety; remarkable clear color contrast.
